{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Ellipse\/font(_:)"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Ellipse"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the default font for text in this view."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"font","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"font","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Font","text":"Font","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4FontV"},{"text":"?) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"font","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default font to use in this view.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view with the default font set to the value you supply."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"code":"font(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply a specific font to all of the text in a view."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The example below shows the effects of applying fonts to i